{"tid":1776567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB員工無盤槊食","createTime":"2019-12-09T15:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T16:26:23.000Z","uid":171506,"like":98,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"27a7693d0793b04b4517bd2d0a777be405305d9c","tid":1776567,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191209/60360397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191209%2F60360397&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=61e5a202\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191209%2F60360397&h=7de16af2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191209/60360397</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫（511，TVB）過去每年12月咁上下嘅時候，都會喺電視城搞一個大型盤菜宴慰勞員工，大家坐埋一齊食飯，董事局成員都會傾巢盡出同大家敬下酒咁，不過今年就仲未有消息，似乎會破天荒延期，員工就憂心忡忡，唔係擔心冇得食，而係可能加人工冇着落。<br />\n<br />\n話說每年TVB主席陳國強同埋行政總裁李寶安都會出席呢個盛事，後者仲會帶喜訊畀大家，講埋加幾多人工，例如2017年宣佈有Bonus兼有2.5%人工升幅；2018年同樣有1個月花紅兼且加人工3%，台下同事通常都會起哄歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，可能社會氣氛唔係咁好，新聞部高層不時因為特別嘅編採方針，畀人揶揄係央媒，前線士氣低落可想而知，最甘嘅係廣告客戶紛紛割席，所以唔好講歡聚晚宴兼有人工加，內部大規模裁員嘅傳聞過去幾個月不逕而走，唔使食無情雞已經要慶賀。"},{"pid":"0f47af2972f758450ec9d8eecabf66c9ad394ac0","tid":1776567,"uid":127553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"879b1a7ba2999cbb6e99795b4757e44e44751029","tid":1776567,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6